36
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:18,780
Did you see our Xiaobao?

37
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,500
He is this tall.

38
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:23,260
He has a mole
on the right side of his face.

39
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,140
He was wearing a white gown

40
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,100
and a pair of white shoes.

41
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:27,500
I was away for a while and you came again.

42
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:29,300
Your grandson is not here.

43
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:30,140
Don't look for him here.

44
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:30,380
He...

45
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,900
They are not from here.

46
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:33,940
They don't know it.

47
00:03:34,460 --> 00:03:35,180
Go out quickly.

48
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,860
Who took away my Xiaobao?

49
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,340
Don't look for him here. 
Your grandson is not here.

50
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,180
Don't come again.

51
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,780
Who is she looking for anyway?

52
