Sorry, everybody.

53
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,740
Sorry.

54
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:46,660
What happened?

55
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,780
She is just a mad woman.

56
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:49,860
Mad as a hatter.

57
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:51,300
She comes every day
to look for her grandson.

58
