The goat soup

60
00:03:54,980 --> 00:03:55,580
will be ready soon.

61
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:56,980
I'll cook it for you now.

62
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:58,220
Sir.

63
00:03:59,620 --> 00:03:59,980
Sir.

64
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:00,780
We don't want the goat soup anymore.

65
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:02,380
Take us directly to our rooms.

66
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:03,180
Okay.

67
00:04:03,740 --> 00:04:04,300
This way, please.

68
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:06,580
Watch your step.

69
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:07,620
This way, please.

70
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:12,580
[Tongfu Inn]

71
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:34,260
It should be right ahead.

72
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,500
Unfortunately, the fog is too heavy.

73
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,180
We can't see anything.

74
