Harder.

82
00:07:56,460 --> 00:07:57,540
Thank you, Sir.

83
00:07:57,820 --> 00:07:59,100
Where are you from?

84
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:00,900
From the direction of Anxi Protectorate.

85
00:08:01,020 --> 00:08:03,060
There was a snowstorm there.

86
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:05,140
I've never seen such a heavy snow.

87
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:07,220
The houses even collapsed
under the weight of the snow.

88
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:10,180
The snowstorm will come soon.

89
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,380
Go north

90
00:08:12,420 --> 00:08:13,100
to Lanfang County.

91
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:13,620
Okay.

92
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,380
I am Di Renjie,
the Magistrate of Lanfang County.

93
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:18,180
If you need help,
go to the Magistrate's Office there.

94
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:20,460
Thank you, Magistrate Di.

95
00:08:20,860 --> 00:08:21,980
Hurry up and go.

96
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:24,900
Thank you, Magistrate.

97
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:31,740
Let's go.

98
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:45,180
What's wrong with your hand?

99
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:48,100
Let me dress your wound.

100
00:08:50,220 --> 00:08:51,340
It is snowing more and more heavily.

101
00:08:51,980 --> 00:08:53,380
Let's not go any further.

102
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,660
Let's go back to Lanfang County.

103
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:20,700
Thickheaded.

104
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:22,260
Today,

105
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:25,500
I'll let you see Di Zhixun
in the netherworld!

106
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:31,460
Father!

107
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,500
Father!

108
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:38,940
Father!

109
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:57,820
Huaiying.

110
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,580
Huaiying.

111
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:09,620
Huaiying.

112
00:11:06,180 --> 00:11:10,060
[Lanfang County Magistrate's Office]

113
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:12,380
Mr. Hong,

114
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:13,460
the wine has been heated.

115
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:14,500
Let's have a drink.

116
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:15,740
How can a girl

117
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:16,860
drink wine?

118
00:11:17,860 --> 00:11:18,620
Give me the bowl.

119
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:19,820
Mr. Hong.

120
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,060
Mr. Hong,

121
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,380
a group of refugees came.

122
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,180
They said it was snowing heavily
in the south.

123
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,340
Will the Magistrate be in danger?

124
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:05,540
[Zhao Yun Library]

125
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,380
Huaiying,

126
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:14,140
there is a library ahead.

127
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:15,620
I'll go take a look.

128
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:17,780
Wait for me for a while.

129
00:12:41,780 --> 00:12:42,500
Coming.

130
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:46,780
I'm sorry to disturb you.

131
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,660
Can I meet Mr. Cui?

132
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:49,620
[Zhou Li]
My teacher ordered

133
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:50,820
that no outsiders should be received.

134
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,380
Wait.

135
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:54,540
The person in the carriage

136
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:56,660
is Di Renjie,
the Magistrate of Lanfang County.

137
00:13:05,620 --> 00:13:06,380
Please wait a minute.

138
00:13:06,860 --> 00:13:07,980
I'll report to my teacher.

139
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:29,700
[Zhao Yun Library]

140
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:38,140
Are you Mr. Cui?

141
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:39,620
No.

142
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:41,300
[Li Miao]
I am Li Miao.

143
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:43,580
The Magistrate and you have come.

144
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:45,140
I should have welcomed you earlier.

145
00:13:45,140 --> 00:13:46,380
Please pardon me.

146
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:50,140
The Magistrate was hurt
by poisonous thorns.

147
00:13:50,380 --> 00:13:51,540
His wound swelled

148
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,300
and he has a fever.

149
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:55,980
Can we spend the night here?

150
00:13:56,820 --> 00:13:58,340
I know a little about medicine.

151
00:13:59,060 --> 00:14:00,380
I can dress the Magistrate's wound.

152
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:02,340
Thank you then.

153
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:03,620
However, Miss,

154
00:14:03,780 --> 00:14:04,700
our teacher, Mr. Cui,

155
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:06,140
was assigned by the Minister of Rites

156
00:14:06,460 --> 00:14:08,500
to compile the local history
of this place.

157
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:10,500
He has been writing in retreat.

158
00:14:10,660 --> 00:14:12,420
Before his retreat, he repeatedly warned

159
00:14:13,180 --> 00:14:15,460
that our library was not convenient
for receiving outsiders.

160
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:17,180
So after the wound is dressed,

161
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:19,220
you have to leave as soon as possible.

162
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:25,540
Follow me.

163
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:39,660
Look,

164
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:41,660
how serious his condition is.

165
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:44,500
So serious.

166
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:47,620
We can't go back to Lanfang County
due to the heavy snow.

167
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:49,340
If you don't take us in,

168
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:51,180
we have nowhere to go tonight.

169
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:54,060
If something really happens
to the Magistrate,

170
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:55,620
you are all responsible.

171
00:14:58,020 --> 00:14:58,420
Hurry.

172
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:00,180
Carry the Magistrate

173
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:01,180
to the library.

174
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:02,140
Yes.

175
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:05,260
Miss Cao, this way.

176
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:13,060
Miss Cao, mind your step.

177
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:14,140
This way, please.

178
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:15,340
Slowly.

179
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:22,780
Miss Cao, here we are.

180
00:15:23,460 --> 00:15:24,900
Our library has no spare rooms for guests.

181
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:28,060
This is where old papers
and books are kept.

182
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,260
You'll have to make do with it.

183
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:33,820
Come.

184
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:35,220
Carry him to the inner room.

185
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,220
Here, yours.

186
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:42,060
Thank you.

187
00:15:42,420 --> 00:15:43,180
Please line up.

188
00:15:45,060 --> 00:15:45,740
Here, yours.

189
00:15:46,180 --> 00:15:46,620
Thank you.

190
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:47,860
[Lanfang County Magistrate's Office]
You see.

191
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,820
I said they shouldn't have gone there.

192
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:51,580
The north of the mountains
and the south of the water are Yin.

193
00:15:51,700 --> 00:15:53,220
How else would they have encountered

194
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,820
such a once-in-a-century snowstorm?

195
00:15:56,140 --> 00:15:57,820
Man proposes, but Heaven disposes.

196
00:15:58,420 --> 00:15:59,500
Fine, Mr. Hong.

197
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,620
Stop nagging.

198
00:16:00,620 --> 00:16:02,060
The Magistrate and Miss Cao will be fine.

199
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:02,940
Let's go.

200
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:05,820
Don't forget to take this.

201
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:07,740
Mount the horse.

202
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,220
Be careful on the road.

203
00:16:16,540 --> 00:16:17,180
Okay!

204
00:17:10,100 --> 00:17:10,860
How is he?

205
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:18,220
The Magistrate's pulse

206
00:17:18,340 --> 00:17:19,540
is disordered.

207
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,300
He was not just poisoned.

208
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,300
He may also have

209
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:25,020
excessive internal heat

210
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:26,460
and has fallen ill from overwork.

211
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:28,700
It doesn't matter.

212
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:31,420
I'll get him some herbs.

213
00:17:31,860 --> 00:17:32,740
Thank you.

214
00:17:37,260 --> 00:17:37,780
Huaiying.

215
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:46,020
Magistrate,

216
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:48,060
you are awake.

217
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:50,020
This is...?

218
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:54,140
I am Li Miao.

219
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:56,780
This place is Zhao Yun Library.

220
00:17:57,140 --> 00:17:59,660
Our teacher is Cui Haoran, Mr. Cui.

221
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:05,500
I've heard

222
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:09,860
Mr. Cui's song in Dingdu.

223
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:11,780
Mr. Cui

224
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:14,300
is kind to others

225
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:16,580
and makes no social distinctions
in teaching.

226
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:19,020
He is a great scholar.

227
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:19,980
Yes.

228
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:24,380
We came rashly...

229
00:18:25,180 --> 00:18:26,700
Help me get up.

230
00:18:27,180 --> 00:18:30,020
I'll go to greet Mr. Cui.

231
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:30,660
Well...

232
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:33,420
Mr. Cui is now in retreat.

233
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:33,940
Yes.

234
00:18:34,540 --> 00:18:35,140
Besides,

235
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,940
Magistrate, your health...

236
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,620
I'm fine.

237
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:41,300
We came rashly.

238
00:18:42,580 --> 00:18:44,180
Help me get up.

239
00:18:55,330 --> 00:18:56,020
This way.

240
00:19:00,130 --> 00:19:00,900
Magistrate,

241
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:03,820
the roads in the library are intricate.

242
00:19:03,900 --> 00:19:05,330
On this snowy night,

243
00:19:05,500 --> 00:19:07,020
the view is even more obstructed.

244
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:10,020
If you need anything,

245
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:12,300
Miss Cao can ask the students
in the library to do it.

246
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:14,780
Don't walk around on your own.

247
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:16,340
Come.

248
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:17,540
Be careful.

249
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:44,700
Why is he burning sandalwood
with such a strong smell?

250
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:48,020
In order to write smoothly

251
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,620
and understand the historical facts,

252
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:52,340
every time after reading
historical materials,

253
00:19:52,700 --> 00:19:54,220
our teacher will be in retreat

254
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:56,340
and focus on meditation.

255
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,580
So he should be burning the sandalwood

256
00:19:59,100 --> 00:19:59,980
to calm his mind.

257
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:02,260
Our teacher

258
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:03,660
repeatedly told us

259
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:05,500
not to disturb him during his retreat.

260
00:20:05,540 --> 00:20:07,140
Otherwise, his previous efforts
would be wasted.

261
00:20:16,260 --> 00:20:16,900
This is...?

262
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:20,620
Eaglewood from Yunshui Lodge.

263
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:21,860
Please give this

264
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:24,380
to Mr. Cui.

265
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,420
I won't disturb him.

266
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,420
Magistrate.

267
00:20:31,780 --> 00:20:32,420
Well,

268
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:33,700
now that you are here,

269
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:35,820
just go in.

270
00:20:42,340 --> 00:20:44,300
I thank you for my teacher.

271
00:20:45,380 --> 00:20:46,700
I'll take this inside for him.

272
00:21:13,420 --> 00:21:14,100
Are you okay?

273
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,700
Magistrate, be careful.

274
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:49,220
Who is it?

275
00:21:55,780 --> 00:21:56,300
Mr. Li.

276
00:21:58,940 --> 00:21:59,780
Zhou Li?

277
00:22:00,260 --> 00:22:01,900
Where are you going?

278
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:05,060
The firewood in Mr. Cui's room
is not burning well.

279
00:22:05,380 --> 00:22:05,860
I

280
00:22:06,220 --> 00:22:07,300
will fetch some firewood.

281
00:22:07,740 --> 00:22:08,340
Fetch some firewood.

282
00:22:08,340 --> 00:22:10,180
I've told you so many times

283
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:12,140
that the woodshed is over there.

284
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:13,980
It's not in this direction.

285
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:16,860
I see.

286
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:18,460
Over there.

287
00:22:18,580 --> 00:22:19,420
Not in this direction.

288
00:22:19,980 --> 00:22:20,700
Not in this direction.

289
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,060
